Package org.omancode.r.types

Java object representations of R matrices, dataframes, and vectors.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CBuildFromREXP
    Builds a Casper dataset from a REXP.
    RDataFrame
    An R expression that is an R dataframe.
    REXPAttr
    Static utility class for getting attributes of REXPs.
    REXPUtil
    Static utility class for working with REXPs.
    RMatrix
    An R expression that is a numeric matrix (ie: a 2D numeric vector).
    RVector
    Represents a vector of a single Java type.
    RVectorList
    A list of RVectors.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UnsupportedTypeException
    Exception that signals that the type is not supported.
